VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT sendStickyBroadcast\s*\(|sendStickyOrderedBroadcast\s*\(
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:putExtra.*(?:token|password|secret|key|data|user|account|credential)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects sticky broadcasts that carry sensitive data in Intent extras.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Sticky Broadcast Carrying Sensitive Data.
